<P>CONTAINING A SKETCH of the MANNERS OF</P>
<LIST>
<ITEM>ITALY,</ITEM>
<ITEM>SWITZERLAND,</ITEM>
<ITEM>FRANCE,</ITEM>
<ITEM>HOLLAND,</ITEM>
<ITEM>AND BRITAIN.</ITEM>
</LIST>
