<P>LIKEWISE, The ADVENTURES of TOM DREADNOUGHT, Who &s;erved as a SOLDIER, and al&s;o as a SAILOR, in the late WAR.</P>
<P>BY OLIVER GOLDSMITH, M. B. Author of the Vicar of Wakefield, &amp;c.</P>
<P>AMERICA: PRINTED FOR EVERY PURCHASER, MDCCLXVIII.</P>
